title: NCT Universe: LASTART
overview: Finally, to find the last fixed members of NCT, the journey of "NCT Universe : LASTART" has set sail. Through fierce training, 10 trainees have climbed up the steps to become candidates. "NCT Universe : LASTART" selects the last NCT debut members. Only 4 can become the final member and make it as NCT with SMROOKIES.
